duties_responsibilities.duty: Assist on Inbound or Outbound activities as requested by the Warehouse Supervisor meeting quality, safety, productivity, and operational standards.
Unload trucks in the Inbound section and use pallet jack or equivalent devices to put pallets out of the trucks.
Use Manhattan Warehouse Management System to check in products.
Store products in warehouse locations using order picker or other devices.
Pick products from warehouse locations and load into outbound trucks.

education_certification.credential: High school degree or GED preferred.
